title: 30 Min ALL STANDING CARDIO ABS Workout | Lose Belly Fat, No Jumping, No Squats, No Repeat
description:
This is a really effective standing abs workout and doesn't include jumps, squats or lunges. Remember to squeeze your muscle while exercising! Let's do this! #nojumpingworkout  #allstanding 

❀Full Body Workout
❀Time: 40 sec on/ 10 sec rest

Calorie Burn 250 - 300 Cal
Warm Up 00:00 - 03:12
Workout 03:12 - 31:35
Cool Down 31:35 - 34:57

*The number of calories you burn will vary from person to person depending on your body composition, workout intensity and also fitness level but this might serve as a guideline.

comments: I did this workout yesterday, today I woke up feeling sore in my sides of my abs/torso - so I guess it’s working 💪🏻✨
Proud of myself for showing up and move my body today…. Thank you Eleni for this amazing workout ❤🥵🫶🏻

I appreciate you making + labeling vids specifically for no jumping and no squatting. It is very difficult for me to find accessible workout videos that I don’t have to constantly modify. I hope one day soon I can build up the core connection to do the higher impact videos but these lower impact ones are absolutely necessary until then so I really commend you for catering to that demographic. And thank you for making them fun!😊
such a good workout. not done much exercise in a while and am trying to get back in shape. this was definitely a great one to start off with. 245 calories down and the sweat is unreal!

Thanks, Eleni! These standing abs, No jumping videos are my go-to’s. Thank you for putting them out frequently. I really like that you change up your moves, but keep the moves similar. I appreciate that you challenge our balance. I’d never do it on my own. I know it’s important. Keep these videos coming. Thanks! 💖
